{"title_page": "Rey Rivera", "text_new": "{{short description|Puerto Rican boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Rey Rivera\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Puerto Rican\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1965|12|14|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Rey Rivera''' (born 14 December 1965) is a Puerto Rican [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Light middleweight|men's light middleweight]] event at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ri/rey-rivera-1.html |title=Rey Rivera Olympic Results |accessdate=5 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rivera, Rey}}\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Puerto Rican male boxers]]\n[[Category:Olympic boxers of Puerto Rico]]\n[[Category:Boxers at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games medalists in boxing]]\n\n\n{{PuertoRico-boxing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Puerto Rican boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Rey Rivera\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Puerto Rican\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1965|12|14|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Rey Rivera''' (born 14 December 1965) is a Puerto Rican [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Light middleweight|men's light middleweight]] event at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athlete