{"title_page": "Lucio Grotone", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Lucio Grotone\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Brazilian\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date|1928|11|9|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo]], Brazil\n| death_date     = {{death date and age|2017|3|20|1928|11|9|df=yes}}\n| death_place    = Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil\n}}\n\n'''Lucio Grotone''' (9 November 1928 &ndash; 20 March 2017) was a Brazilian [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1952 Summer Olympics \u2013 Light heavyweight|men's light heavyweight]] event at the [[1952 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/gr/lucio-grottone-1.html |title=Lucio Grotone Olympic Results |accessdate=18 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Grotone, Lucio}}\n[[Category:1928 births]]\n[[Category:2017 deaths]]\n[[Category:Brazilian male boxers]]\n[[Category:Olympic boxers of Brazil]]\n[[Category:Boxers at the 1952 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games medalists in boxing]]\n\n\n{{Brazil-boxing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Lucio Grotone\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Brazilian\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date|1928|11|9|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo]], Brazil\n| death_date     = {{death date and age|2017|3|20|1928|11|9|df=yes}}\n| death_place    = Santos, S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil\n}}\n\n'''Lucio Grotone''' (9 November 1928 &ndash; 20 March 2017) was a Brazilian [[boxing|boxer]]. He compe